name: Jeff Thompson
text: I was informed this business sold auto sound equipment, they don't. They might in the future but for now it's only musical instruments, speakers, and such. I can't rate something I don't use but I had to pick a number so I thought the more colorful the more attractive (lol). I will say the employee was very nice and commented they get a lot of request for auto sound equipment. Maybe down the road they'll install car stereos?

Lots of sound reinforcement stuff too. Prices looked reasonable. I was told that the stock rotates pretty fast too.Stop by and check 'em out.
